title: Family Guy - The Game BETA!
description:
New Family Guy game. (similar to Simpsons Tapped out)

Game is unreleased at the moment, its only been released to us beta testers. so here it is, enjoy it before anyone else.


There are 4 APK files, you only need ONE. However depending on your device will depend on which one works for you.
so try them in order, 1 first if that crashes, uninstall then install 2 etc..

If you get the error: "Plist Retina Texture Not Found: " then copy the images in the tiles directory to sdcard/Android/data/com.tinyco.familyguy.beta (if you don't get the error then no need for these files)



Game is BETA!! so its as-is.. if it doesn't work for you then wait for the release.




Send your blessings to FlamerFTW
